cfengine 

Built upon well-established theory and high-quality engineering   
practices, CFEngine has enjoyed an outstanding security record over 
its 19-year history. 

CFEngine solutions are highly scalable through decentralized, 
autonomous agents that can continuously monitor, self-repair, and 
update a global multi-site enterprise every five minutes -- 
with negligible impact on system resources or performance.

CFEngine Community is licensed under the Gnu General Public License 
GPL, version 3 and available as a free-of charge download or in 
source form

